She stopped her running and responded to BlackStorm. "listen, check 
the bot's frequency. If it's close to ours, then it's a pred.

transformed into wolf mode. Her face was covered in fur and her face 
plates were dry now. She dashed back past SharpClaw and towards 
Blackstorm. "Hang on, I'm on my way."
